Package org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.sdbw

Class RandomSDBW

java.lang.Object
org.svvrl.goal.core.AbstractGenerator<T>
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.AbstractRandomAutomaton<FSA>
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.sdbw.RandomSDBW
All Implemented Interfaces:
Generator<FSA>
public class RandomSDBW
extends AbstractRandomAutomaton<FSA>
This class provides a generator for semi-deterministic Büchi word automata (SDBW). In an SDBW, the states are partitioned into two disjoint sets N and D where D is deterministic and accepting states are all included in D.
Author:
"Ming-Hsien Tsai"
